                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Mel- Frequency cepstral coefficients: The first method is a widely- used technique for acoustic- applications [33], in particular, to capture relevant characteristics of the human auditory system by transforming the audio signal into a compact representation with a user- defined number, denoted as "
                                },
                                {
