                                    "bbox": [
                                        1269,
                                        1712,
                                        2319,
                                        2352
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " values from 10 to 50. By extracting a relatively small number of coefficients, MFCCs reduce the dimensionality of the feature space while retaining essential information about the audio signal. This is crucial for efficient processing and classification. The MFCC extraction is done on each audio chunk of the dataset, this process is explained by the following sequence of steps necessary to obtain the MFCC coefficients vector."
